text: Toomas Vilpart (born 21 September 1971) is an Estonian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Estonian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Estonia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Viljandi
